#: ../content/index.rst:7
msgid "This extension facilitates communication between system addresses within OTOBO (e.g. in cc), by defining address pools which are treated as separate entities in the system. Mails sent to multiple pools create an article in every pool, associated tickets are linked and will be used to assign FollowUps."
msgstr ""

